    • dimensionTeleportShip

      public static void dimensionTeleportShip(org.valkyrienskies.core.api.ships.Ship ship, net.minecraft.server.level.ServerLevel level, String newDim, double x, double y, double z)
      Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
      This function took us like a week days to make. You better appreciate it.

      It will teleport the given ship, using the level, to the dimension with id of newDim at x, y, z.

      But most importantly, it will also teleport any players or entities (including create contraptions) that are currently being dragged by the ship to the new dimension, and their correct position relative to the ship that was moved.
      Parameters:
      ship - The ship to move
      level - The ships current level
      newDim - Normal dimension id string format (not VS format)
      x - x position in world to tp the ship to
      y - y position in world to tp the ship to
      z - z position in world to tp the ship to
